WEBVTT

00:04.320 --> 00:05.635
Hey, I'm off to the mall.

00:05.755 --> 00:07.323
What do you do there every day?

00:07.443 --> 00:08.747
You don't have any money.

00:08.867 --> 00:09.830
I don't need money.

00:09.950 --> 00:11.796
I go to the food court
and eat free samples.

00:17.860 --> 00:19.394
Are you looking for your purse?

00:19.396 --> 00:21.162
It's in the closet.

00:21.164 --> 00:23.965
It's a handbag, not a purse.

00:23.967 --> 00:25.767
Why don't you just carry a wallet?

00:25.769 --> 00:28.260
And what am I supposed
to do with all my items?

00:28.262 --> 00:30.672
What items?

00:30.674 --> 00:32.430
My phone,

00:32.433 --> 00:33.827
sunglasses,

00:33.829 --> 00:36.338
my mints, my lip gloss,

00:36.340 --> 00:37.768
my scrunchies.

00:37.770 --> 00:38.902
Ugh.
I can't believe

00:38.904 --> 00:40.369
you go out looking like that.

00:40.371 --> 00:42.366
You're right.

00:46.608 --> 00:56.715
Corrections by honeybunny
Sync by www.addic7ed.com

00:58.000 --> 01:04.074
